              ]
            }
          ],
          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The target was a foil of 197Au, 500 microg/cm2 thick,",
                "mounted at 15 degree to the beam."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "DETECTOR": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "SI",
                "SCIN"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                ""
              ]
            }
          ],
          "METHOD": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "COINC",
                "TOF"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " Coincident heavy fragments emitted at",
                "about 90 degree to the beam were detected in two",
                "arrays of Si detectors on either side of the beam,",
                "and their energies and velocities measured to",
                "determine their masses. A separate large-area",
                "avalanche detector for each array provided the start",
                "signal for the time-of-flight measurement. In",
                "coincidence with each binary event, the associated",
                "multiplicity of fast charged particles was measured",
                "by means of 80 plastic scintillators which were",
                "mounted outside the spherical, thin-walled scatter",
                "chamber, thus providing a measure of the degree of",
                "violence of the interaction."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "EN-SEC": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "ANG1: Angle beam - heavy fragment",
                "ANG-RL: Correlation angle"
              ]
            }
          ],
          "ERR-ANALYS": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "heading": "DATA-ERR1",
                "minimum_value": null,
                "maximum_value": null,
                "correlation_property": null
              },
              "free_text": [
                " The absolute normalization of the cross",
                "section scale has an uncertainty of about 30%."
              ]
            },
